Integration Orchestration now has a prebuilt Lightning Web Component. Add this component to your record page to give users a consolidated view of all the integration callouts. Users can easily manage manual and automatically triggered integrations—all at one place.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Professional, Enterprise, and Unlimited editions where Financial Services Cloud is enabled.

How: In the Lightning App Builder, add the Integration Execution Status component to the record page.
